channel.title: DISKOmUnIST Podcast
channel.description:
DISKOmUnIST... brings you DISCOmoonICATION...a new DJ set every fullmoon featuring a lunar selection of house, minimal and tech-house tracks...
additionally look for the exclusive series: DISCOloration - which delves towards the minimal...comes in some new moons...* Deep State - an exclusive deep house series that comes once in a while also new exclusive series will be featured soon as well, so stay tuned*
DISKOmUnIST is the DJ monicker of musician/producer Cihan Baris.
channel.itunes:subtitle: house tech minimal deep tribal
